item.title: Thunder Rabbit
item.description: 23:06 Saturday 15 October 2016 AWST Today is the day I was like, “I’m feeling a bit cheeky, and I’m jealous of him getting so much attention. I’m Thunder Rabbit and I’m never ever ever going to change my name, and my name is still Thunder Rabbit!”
